    "wizard_lang_input": "Type a мови name and press Ввести or натиснути + to додати it for multilingual generation. Up to 4 мови can be added.",
    "wizard_lang_input_title": "мови ввід",
    "wizard_interest_input": "Додати учні interests (e.g., soccer, dinosaurs, space) to personalize створено вміст. The AI weaves these into приклади and analogies for higher engagement.",
